 expressed in words',inevitable:'Certain to happen',inexplicable:'Unable to be explained',infatuation:'Intense short-lived passion',infrastructure:'Basic systems of a society',insurmountable:'Too great to overcome',interdependence:'Mutual reliance between things',introspective:'Examining one\'s own thoughts',iridescent:'Showing rainbow-like colours',irrevocable:'Cannot be changed or undone',juggernaut:'Unstoppable crushing force',jurisdiction:'Official legal power or territory',laborious:'Requiring much effort',lachrymose:'Tearful or causing tears',loquacious:'Tending to talk a great deal','magnanimous':'Noble and generous in spirit',malfeasance:'Wrongdoing by a public official',manipulation:'Controlling someone unfairly',meticulous:'Showing great attention to detail',millennium:'Period of one thousand years',miscreant:'Person who behaves badly',monumental:'Of great importance or size',morphology:'Study of forms and structures',multifaceted:'Having many aspects',nefarious:'Wicked and criminal',nomenclature:'System of names or terms',nonplussed:'So surprised as to be unsure',obfuscation:'Making something unclear',obsolescence:'Process of becoming outdated',omnipotent:'Having unlimited power',oppression:'Prolonged cruel treatment',oscillation:'Regular back and forth movement',ostentatious:'Designed to impress others',paradoxical:'Seemingly contradictory but true',paraphernalia:'Miscellaneous articles or equipment',pathological:'Relating to disease or obsession',peculiarity:'Unusual characteristic',perplexity:'State of being confused',perseverance:'Persistence despite difficulty',philanthropist:'One who promotes human welfare',philosophical:'Relating to deep thinking',photosynthesis:'Plants making food from sunlight',physiological:'Relating to body functions',polarization:'Division into opposing groups',preposterous:'Absurd and contrary to reason',prestigious:'Inspiring respect and admiration',proliferation:'Rapid spread or increase',protagonist:'Main character of a st